### Public (sin token)
GET http://localhost:8081/public/health

### List rules (token válido: cualquier usuario)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get by id (token válido)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/rules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create (solo ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rule A",
  "description": "Test",
  "isActive": true
}

### Toggle (solo ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/rules/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
